  "headline": "206 of 6,840 currently-active federally-excluded NPIs (across 52 state cohorts) billed Medicare Part B in CY 2023 (full-window total paid $30,770,165 on 635,144 services). Of those, **5 were billing STRICTLY POST-EXCLUSION** (LEIE or SAM exclusion-effective year before 2023), with $2,022,667 paid on 116,552 services. The strict-post-exclusion subset is the regulatorily significant signal under 42 USC \u00a7 1320a-7 \u2014 pre-exclusion billing reflects work the provider was authorized to do at the time.",
